 [FILES] President Muhammadu Buhari  In a statement, yesterday by his Senior Special Assistant on Media and Publicity, Garba Shehu, the president said: “I have lost a prudent and wonderful custodian who did so well taking care of my country home in Daura. May Allah bless his soul and give strength to the bereaved family to bear this irreparable loss.” The president sent a delegation to the bereaved family in Sandamu Council of Katsina, comprising Senior Special Assistant, Domestic and Household Matters, Sarki Abba; State Chief of Protocol, Amb. Lawal Kazaure; and Shehu. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .